source.name: DRCOG Crash Data Points 2006
source.description: This file contains a record for each reported traffic crash in the Region. The crash record provides information on the date, time, collision type, vehicle type, driver demographics, and contributing factors for each crash. The data originates from State of Colorado Traffic Accident Report Forms.
